            <h3>State-of-the-Art Facilities</h3>
            <p>Aatura Hospital is equipped with advanced technology and state-of-the-art facilities to support our Gastroenterology Department's efforts. From our endoscopy suites and imaging facilities to our on-site laboratory and pathology services, we have the resources needed to provide high-quality diagnostic and treatment services for gastrointestinal conditions.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content3">
        <div class="cl">
            <h3>Patient-Centered Care</h3>
            <p>At Aatura Hospital, we prioritize patient-centered care, focusing on the individual needs and concerns of each patient. Our gastroenterologists take the time to listen to patients' symptoms, answer their questions, and involve them in decision-making regarding their gastrointestinal health. We strive to create a comfortable and supportive environment where patients feel heard, respected, and empowered to participate in their care.</p>
        </div>
